    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the steak is cooking, return the pot to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained green beans</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further – these are your <strong>garlicky green beans</strong></p>",
