      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested sirloin steak </strong>finely on a clean board</p><p>Served the <strong>sliced sirloin steak</strong> with the <strong>dauphinoise potatoes</strong> and <strong>garlicky green beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Pour the <strong>redcurrant sauce</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
